---
// Dwarf-themed geomantic weather widget for sidebar
---
<div class="sidebarBox">
  <h4>GEOMANTIC CONDITIONS</h4>
  <div class="sidebarContent weatherWidget">
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Zone</th>
        <th>Status</th>
        <th>Temp</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Surface</td>
        <td><span class="wxCaution">BLIZZARD</span></td>
        <td>-14°S</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Z-1 to Z-10</td>
        <td><span class="wxStable">STABLE</span></td>
        <td>58°S</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Z-11 to Z-30</td>
        <td><span class="wxStable">STABLE</span></td>
        <td>62°S</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Z-31 to Z-50</td>
        <td><span class="wxCaution">ADVISORY</span></td>
        <td>65°S</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Z-51 to Z-80</td>
        <td><span class="wxStable">STABLE</span></td>
        <td>71°S</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Z-81 to Z-100</td>
        <td><span class="wxCaution">MONITOR</span></td>
        <td>84°S</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Z-101+ (Magma)</td>
        <td><span class="wxAlert">ELEVATED</span></td>
        <td>340°S</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <div style="margin-top:6px; border-top:1px solid #ddd; padding-top:4px;">
      <strong>Seismic Index:</strong> 1.2 (Low)<br/>
      <strong>Magma Pressure:</strong> 12% of capacity<br/>
      <strong>Aquifer Level:</strong> Normal<br/>
      <strong>Surface Wind:</strong> 45 kn NW
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:4px; font-size:9px; color:#cc0000;">
      &#9888; Z-Level 45 Advisory remains active.<br/>
      &#9888; Surface trade routes CLOSED.
    </div>
    <div class="wxUpdate">
      Updated: Mar 11, 312 | 9:00 PM<br/>
      Source: Geomancer's Office
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
